OL,3,CNewcastle United announce plans for
OL,4,Chonouring Kevin Keegan
OL,6,FNewcastle United have today (23 July)
OL,7,Frevealed plans to honour the legacy of
OL,8,Fclub legend Kevin Keegan, who died
OL,9,Fearlier this week at the age of 75.
OL,11,FSince his death, many fans have been
OL,12,Fcalling for a statue of 'King Kev' to
OL,13,Fbe erected outside St James' Park.
OL,15,FThe club have said they will consult
OL,16,Fwith Kevin's family "at the
OL,17,Fappropriate time" about plans for a
OL,18,Fpermanent tribute.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/5
