OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1784836083
OL,3,CNewcastle United announce plans for
OL,4,Chonouring Kevin Keegan
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Newcastle United's men's,
OL,7,Fwomen's and under-21s teams will wear
OL,8,Fblack armbands during all of their pre-
OL,9,Fseason matches this summer.
OL,11,FAnd, details have also been released
OL,12,Fof other ways in which Keegan will be
OL,13,Fhonoured during pre-season.
OL,15,FOn Saturday (25 July), when Newcastle
OL,16,FUnited's men's team play their first
OL,17,Fgame since Keegan's passing - a
OL,18,Ffriendly against Gateshead, there will
OL,19,Fbe a minute's silence before the
OL,20,Fmatch, and both teams will wear black
OL,21,Farmbands.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1784836083
OL,3,CNewcastle United announce plans for
OL,4,Chonouring Kevin Keegan
OL,6,FThen on Wednesday 29 July, during the
OL,7,FMagpies' away game at Bristol City,
OL,8,FKevin's image will be shown on the
OL,9,Fstadium's screens during the 7th
OL,10,Fminute, a nod to the number he wore
OL,11,Fduring his playing career. Supporters
OL,12,Fare encouraged to honour him with a
OL,13,Fminute's applause at this time.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
