CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1784836084
OL,3,CNewcastle United announce plans for
OL,4,Chonouring Kevin Keegan
OL,6,FDuring the 'Visit Malta Weekender' at
OL,7,FSt James' Park on 15 and 16 August,
OL,8,Fwhen the men's team will play Bayer
OL,9,FLeverkusen and Strasbourg, and the
OL,10,Fwomen's team will play Inter Milan,
OL,11,FKevin's image will again be shown on
OL,12,Fscreen during the 7th minute of each
OL,13,Ffixutre.
OL,15,FNewcastle United's opening game of the
OL,16,F2026/27 Premier League season will
OL,17,Fappropriately see them host Liverpool,
OL,18,Fthe club where Keegan spent much of
OL,19,Fhis playing career.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/5
